1
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:10,000
Tawan's single. She's not dating.

2
00:00:10,080 --> 00:00:11,320
Really?

3
00:00:12,160 --> 00:00:13,840
Where is she now?

4
00:00:15,080 --> 00:00:18,760
Asleep. Her people are taking care of me.

5
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:22,240
You know, I'm still excited.

6
00:00:23,400 --> 00:00:25,560
What about you? Are you okay?

7
00:00:26,280 --> 00:00:27,360
Not really.

8
00:00:28,120 --> 00:00:30,480
Because she got hurt, right?

9
00:00:30,480 --> 00:00:31,440
Yeah.

10
00:00:32,439 --> 00:00:35,440
I feel bad for her. Getting hurt like this.

11
00:00:36,040 --> 00:00:39,640
Hey, she's working as your bodyguard,

12
00:00:39,720 --> 00:00:42,240
so she has to do her job.

13
00:00:42,480 --> 00:00:45,440
Besides, if something happened to you,

14
00:00:45,440 --> 00:00:47,640
your dad would totally kill her.

15
00:00:47,720 --> 00:00:52,040
Ugh, we just reunited a few days ago
and there's already trouble.

16
00:00:52,600 --> 00:00:56,120
Hey, anyway, does your dad know?

17
00:00:56,640 --> 00:00:58,040
Of course not.

18
00:00:58,520 --> 00:01:01,360
I don't want him to know.
He'd made me go home for sure.

19
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:03,440
Well, that's true.

20
00:01:05,519 --> 00:01:07,840
At least you're unharmed.

21
00:01:08,280 --> 00:01:10,480
Your dad probably won't do anything to her.

22
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:14,680
Honestly, I'm so confused right now.

23
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:19,080
On one hand, I'm happy to
have her around, taking care of me.

24
00:01:19,080 --> 00:01:21,520
But on the other hand, when I see her get hurt,

25
00:01:21,600 --> 00:01:26,040
I feel like I don't want her to come to any harm.
You get the picture, right?

26
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:30,640
And these people trying to hurt me, I have no idea
who they are and why they hate me so much.

27
00:01:30,720 --> 00:01:33,160
And I don't know what's in store for me in the future.

28
00:01:33,160 --> 00:01:36,600
Hey, calm down, Ms. Idol.

29
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:39,760
Get it together. Focus.

30
00:01:40,080 --> 00:01:44,240
Can you trust anyone else but Tawan right now, Ayla?

31
00:01:44,320 --> 00:01:47,920
You should be glad she agreed to
take this job of taking care of you.

32
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:50,240
But I'm worried about her.

33
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:51,800
Yeah, I know that.

34
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:54,280
You worry about her and love her so much.

35
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:56,240
I've been listening to this since Grade 10.

36
00:01:56,680 --> 00:02:00,360
Hey, if you're worried about her,
then go take good care of her.

37
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:03,120
Maybe she'll give in.

38
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:33,640
Actually, Boss works very hard

39
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:36,160
to get the company to this point.

40
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:41,760
And almost all the VIPs who worked with her before
don't want to deal with other companies.

41
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:43,520
That's true.

42
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,760
We're just telling you, not bragging.

43
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:48,680
Her standards are extremely high.

44
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:52,280
If someone mentions her name,
people in the industry know that

45
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:55,360
she's a perfectionist and doesn't make mistakes.

46
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:59,080
Being thorough, detail-oriented and observant

47
00:03:59,160 --> 00:04:00,960
leads to successful jobs.

48
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:03,760
We've been following her principles.

49
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:05,760
And our jobs have been successful.

50
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:11,160
Boss told me that
doing our best to protect other people

51
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:13,800
was a beginning of our duties as bodyguards.

52
00:04:46,280 --> 00:04:47,280
Tawan.

53
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,240
Ms. Ayla?

54
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:17,000
You should sleep in your room.

55
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:20,400
Please let me sleep here.

56
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:24,280
It's better to sleep in your room.

57
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:28,000
If she wakes up and sees you sleep here,

58
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:31,040
we'll definitely be punished.
